      <h4>About<b> GKTCS Innovations</b></h4>
      <br />
      <p>Today’s world is a highly competitive world and almost all organisation’s are exposed to best raw materials, supply chains, marketing and cost control opinions etc. But the human resource is the most important of all the assets. To improve the competency and capability of human resource. Training and development has become an integrated part of any organisations to do list. Just like we add manure to nurture the plant which would give fruits. In similar manner we need to add manure to human resources by the way of training to deliver desired results.</p>
      <p>GKTCS Innovations is a result of professionals from training and development coming together with a common vision “to deliver most optimized training solutions to the organisation which are result oriented and cost effective”. GKTCS Innovation has an average experience of 7+ years in the field of Training and Development. GKTCS Innovation has a desire to be the # 1 , Corporate Service providers in diversified fields and is backed up by ability and willingness to do it.</p>
      <p>GKTCS Innovations is headquartered in the IT city of India, Pune better known as Oxford of the East. We have one of the biggest database of trainers in IT, Non – IT and Soft Skills Trainer and guarantee you the best TURN AROUND TIME and Higher Standards of Training. GKTCS is an innovative and ever growing organisation that believes in TTT (Transformation Through Training).</p>
      <p>We have been into training and development since 2008, and now transformed into GKTCS Innovations as the result of continual improvement. We have successfully delivered more than 150 + trainings in IT and 60 + trainings in NON IT across 14 domestic and 6 international locations. We have 400 + certified trainers from 6 MNC who are delivering the training across India and Abroad.</p>
      <p>GKTCS Innovations has been delivering higher standards of training right from fresher to senior level managers. We are proud to inform you that, since inception we have not been marked less than 100 % on delivery standards, 98 % on- time delivery and always have a backup trainer ready for all training on and off chart.</p>
      <p><b>“Think beyond Success”</b></p>
